              === WELCOME TO RIFTS EARTH MUD ===

This is a roleplaying game set in the world of Rifts by Palladium Books.
The setting is Earth, hundreds of years in the future, after catastrophic
dimensional rifts tore reality apart.  Magic, technology, and aliens coexist
in a dangerous and unpredictable world.

Getting started:
  - You are in Praxis, a survivor settlement in the former American Midwest.
  - Talk to the Survivor in the welcome room.  Type: say hello
  - Explore Monument Square to the south.  Type: south
  - Use 'look' to examine your surroundings at any time.
  - Use 'help' for a list of available commands.
  - Use 'score' to view your character's stats.

Roleplay notes:
  - This game uses a language system.  Type 'language' to see your languages.
  - Different races speak different languages by default.
  - You can learn new languages through practice and training.

Stay aware of your surroundings.  The world outside Praxis is dangerous.

